===樓宇===
====廣田邨====
邨內設有4座大廈，主要由房屋署建築師負責屋邨總體設計，並且聘請王歐陽（香港）有限公司共同負責屋邨設計<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=The Evolution of Housing Authority's Standard Block Designs and Procurement of Professional Services Provider for Public Housing Development|url=https://www.hkia.net/UserFiles/Image/General%20Meetings/2011_3_QGM_speaker_ppt.pdf|author=香港建築師學會|date=2011-03|format=PDF|pages=P.10|access-date=2021-10-28|archive-date=2022-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408081117/https://www.hkia.net/UserFiles/Image/General%20Meetings/2011_3_QGM_speaker_ppt.pdf}}</ref>。當中廣靖樓是全港首座和諧三型大廈，亦為全港首座竣工的和諧式大廈<ref>[https://www.hkmapservice.gov.hk/OneStopSystem/map-search/getPreviewFile?itemId=DAP&sheetNo=A32777 1992年10月廣田邨及油塘邨航空照片]</ref>。

